{"id":2885,"date":"2020-02-10T15:47:53","date_gmt":"2020-02-10T08:47:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/?p=2885"},"modified":"2020-02-11T17:12:43","modified_gmt":"2020-02-11T10:12:43","slug":"tai-sao-rem-cua-2-lop-duoc-ua-chuong-nhat-hien-nay","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/tai-sao-rem-cua-2-lop-duoc-ua-chuong-nhat-hien-nay.html","title":{"rendered":"T\u1ea1i Sao R\u00e8m C\u1eeda 2 L\u1edbp \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01afa Chu\u1ed9ng Nh\u1ea5t Hi\u1ec7n Nay?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-hai-lop\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">R\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp<\/span><\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"> \u0111\u1eb9p sang tr\u1ecdng \u0111ang l\u00e0 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eabu r\u00e8m hot nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m nay, B\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 uy t\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafp \u0111\u1eb7t r\u00e8m c\u1eeda cho kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh, H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ebfn ngay v\u1edbi<a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"> R\u00e8m Ph\u00fa Th\u00e0nh<\/span><\/a> l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ty h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c R\u00e8m c\u1eeda, Gi\u1ea5y d\u00e1n t\u01b0\u1eddng, Th\u1ea3m tr\u1ea3i s\u00e0n, \u2026 V\u1edbi h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean gia t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n l\u00e2u n\u0103m trong ng\u00e0nh, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf tr\u00ean to\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt m\u1eabu m\u00e3 v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean sang tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2743 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-20-2-491x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1298\" height=\"1058\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-20-2-491x400.jpg 491w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-20-2-510x416.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/rem-hl-20-2.jpg 708w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1298px) 100vw, 1298px\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i 2 l\u1edbp sang tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><strong>R\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-hai-lop\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">R\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp<\/span><\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ki\u1ec3u r\u00e8m c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb \u0111ang r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0a th\u00edch v\u00ec ki\u1ec3u d\u00e1ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 t\u00ednh n\u0103ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i. R\u00e8m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o t\u1eeb 2 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i, m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u c\u1ea3n n\u1eafng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1t. V\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i m\u1ecfng c\u1ea3n b\u1ee7i, v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n nh\u1eefng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng nh\u1eb9 n\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m t\u1eeb v\u1ea3i voan, l\u1ee5a, ren,\u2026 C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 che ch\u1eafn \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, l\u00e0m m\u00e1t cho c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8, v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u1ea5m v\u00e0o m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng. Khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00e1nh n\u1eafng qu\u00e1 g\u1eaft th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e9n l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i voan m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9 b\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quan s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3nh v\u1eadt b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2886 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaitholamrem2lop-502x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1311\" height=\"1045\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaitholamrem2lop-502x400.jpg 502w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaitholamrem2lop-510x406.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaitholamrem2lop-768x612.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaitholamrem2lop-1005x800.jpg 1005w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaitholamrem2lop.jpg 1689w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1311px) 100vw, 1311px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>L\u1edbp v\u1ea3i b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i l\u00e0 l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1t<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2887 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvoan2lop-328x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1302\" height=\"1587\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvoan2lop-328x400.jpg 328w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvoan2lop-510x623.jpg 510w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1302px) 100vw, 1302px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>L\u1edbp v\u1ea3i b\u00ean trong l\u00e0 l\u1edbp voan tr\u1eafng m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><strong>C\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i may r\u00e8m c\u1eeda<em><br \/>\n<\/em><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\"><em><span style=\"color: #333399;\"><strong>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i l\u1ee5a<\/strong><\/span><\/em>: V\u1ea3i l\u1ee5a l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m t\u1eeb t\u1edd t\u1eb1m, r\u1ea5t tr\u01a1n v\u00e0 m\u1ecfng. R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i l\u1ee5a c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. L\u1ee5a t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1eeb t\u01a1 t\u1eb1m l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i l\u1ee5a cao c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay. T\u1eeb xa x\u01b0a v\u1ea3i l\u1ee5a \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i c\u1ef1c ph\u1ea9m trong \u0111\u1eddi s\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y. L\u1ee5a l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng\u00a0 \u0111\u1ec3 may qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o, ch\u0103n ga g\u1ed1i hay may nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu r\u00e8m c\u1eeda cao c\u1ea5p sang tr\u1ecdng. N\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng. \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng khi d\u00f9ng v\u1ea3i l\u1ee5a \u0111\u1ec3 may r\u00e8m d\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng gian sang tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Do v\u1ea3i lua m\u1ecfng nh\u1eb9 n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c v\u1ec7 sinh r\u00e8m c\u0169ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2888 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvailua-368x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1302\" height=\"1415\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvailua-368x400.jpg 368w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvailua-510x555.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvailua.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1302px) 100vw, 1302px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i l\u1ee5a l\u00e0m r\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong><em><span style=\"font-size: 110%; color: #333399;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i Cotton:<\/span><\/em><\/strong> <span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ec7t t\u1eeb nguy\u00ean li\u1ec7u thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean. V\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m t\u1eeb hcaats li\u1ec7u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c t\u00ednh mau kh\u00f4, h\u00fat \u1ea9m, t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng, m\u00e1t v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u00e0 \u1ea5m v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a \u0111\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i cho vi\u1ec7c may ga g\u1ed1i, r\u00e8m c\u1eeda,&#8230;<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2890 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvairemcotton-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1290\" height=\"1290\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvairemcotton-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvairemcotton-510x510.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvairemcotton-280x280.jpg 280w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvairemcotton-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvairemcotton.jpg 800w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvairemcotton-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1290px) 100vw, 1290px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i cotton may r\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 110%; color: #333399;\"><em><strong>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i Polyesste:<\/strong> <\/em><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">Polyeste l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c t\u1eeb than \u0111\u00e1, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed, n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u m\u1ecf, s\u1ee3i v\u1ea3i polyeste \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh t\u1eeb ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc gi\u1eefa acid v\u00e0 r\u01b0\u1ee3u. H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i r\u00e8m c\u1eeda tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c may b\u1eb1ng v\u1ea3i Polyeste l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu v\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a n\u00f3 nh\u01b0: may r\u00e8m b\u1eb1ng v\u1ea3i Polyeste c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n cao, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb bay m\u00e0u. Lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb co gi\u00e3n, \u0111\u00e0n h\u1ed3i, kh\u00f4ng nh\u0103n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh r\u1ebb. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3 c\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0 n\u1eb7ng, d\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-2891 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaipolyestelamrem2lop-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1312\" height=\"1312\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaipolyestelamrem2lop-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaipolyestelamrem2lop-510x510.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaipolyestelamrem2lop-280x280.jpg 280w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaipolyestelamrem2lop-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaipolyestelamrem2lop-800x800.jpg 800w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaipolyestelamrem2lop-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaipolyestelamrem2lop.jpg 991w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1312px) 100vw, 1312px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i Polyeste \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n cao, ch\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5m t\u1ed1t<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #333399;\"><strong><em>R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i nhung:<\/em> <\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">V\u1ea3i nhung l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u sang tr\u1ecdng, m\u1ecbn, m\u01b0\u1ee3t, x\u1ed1p,c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u1ea5m nh\u01b0 len nh\u01b0ng m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 qu\u00fd ph\u00e1i. \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i nhung l\u00e0 ti\u00eau \u00e2m, c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf n\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong ph\u00f2ng h\u00e1t gia \u0111\u00ecnh, trong c\u00e1c h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1edbn, r\u1ea1p h\u00e1t, s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u00e0o m\u00f2n th\u1ea5p n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng may b\u1ecdc gh\u1ebf sofa sang tr\u1ecdng. Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a v\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 n\u1eb7ng, d\u1ec5 co gi\u00e3n v\u00e0 b\u00e1m b\u1ee5i. v\u1ec7 sinh gi\u1eb7t m\u1edbi r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2894 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvainhunglamrem2lop-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1306\" height=\"1306\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvainhunglamrem2lop-400x400.jpg 400w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvainhunglamrem2lop-510x510.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvainhunglamrem2lop-280x280.jpg 280w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvainhunglamrem2lop-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvainhunglamrem2lop-800x800.jpg 800w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvainhunglamrem2lop-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvainhunglamrem2lop.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1306px) 100vw, 1306px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i nhung c\u00e1ch \u00e2m, c\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1t<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%; color: #333399;\"><strong><em>R\u00e8m c\u1eeda v\u1ea3i B\u1ed1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i:<\/em><\/strong><\/span> <span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">V\u1ea3i b\u1ed1 t\u00ean g\u1ecdi kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 v\u1ea3i Canvas l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i d\u1ec7t th\u00f4 th\u1eddi c\u1ed5 th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00f9ng c\u00e2y gai. Lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i n\u00e0y d\u00e0y, th\u00f4 tr\u01a1n, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 hoa v\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng m\u00e0u s\u1eafc \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. M\u1eb7t v\u1ea3i th\u00f4 s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i kh\u00f4ng b\u00f3ng m\u1ecbn. Trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf may r\u00e8m, v\u1ea3i b\u1ed1 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p cho kh\u00f4ng gian hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n trong \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf. Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ee3i v\u1ea3i th\u01b0a, \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ea3n s\u00e1ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng cao, d\u1ec5 b\u00e1m b\u1ee5i<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2895 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaibolamrem2lop-543x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1329\" height=\"979\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaibolamrem2lop-543x400.jpg 543w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaibolamrem2lop-510x375.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/chatlieuvaibolamrem2lop.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1329px) 100vw, 1329px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i b\u1ed1 d\u00e0y d\u1eb7n, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 120%;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: #333399;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i voan:<\/span> <\/em><\/strong><\/span><span style=\"font-size: 90%;\">v\u1ea3i voan th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 1 lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n g\u00f4c t\u1eeb s\u1ee3i nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o, mang l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c bay b\u1ed5ng. T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ebfn nay r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i voan ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n. \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u voan l\u00e0 gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh r\u1ebb, th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp v\u1ea3i d\u00e0y t\u1ea1o n\u00ean b\u1ed9 <a href=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/danh-muc\/rem-hai-lop\/\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">r\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp<\/span><\/a> sang tr\u1ecdng. H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e0m r\u00e8m c\u1eeda v\u1ea3i voan ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng v\u00e0 kem. Ngo\u00e0i ra r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i voan c\u00f3 th\u00eau c\u00e1c hoa v\u0103n r\u1ea5t phong ph\u00fa<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-1882 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/9d7dc28ceb760d285467-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1353\" height=\"1016\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/9d7dc28ceb760d285467-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/9d7dc28ceb760d285467-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/9d7dc28ceb760d285467-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/9d7dc28ceb760d285467-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/9d7dc28ceb760d285467.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1353px) 100vw, 1353px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>Ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u v\u1ea3i voan m\u1ec1n, m\u1ecfng, nh\u1eb9, l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n\u00a0<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 130%;\"><strong>C\u00e1c ki\u1ec3u may r\u00e8m th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng cho r\u00e8m v\u1ea3i 2 l\u1edbp\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 110%;\"><strong><em><span style=\"color: #000080;\">R\u00e8m v\u1ea3i may Ore, Voan may chi\u1ebft ly<\/span><\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-995 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/1c4b4f02b114574a0e05-533x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1293\" height=\"970\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/1c4b4f02b114574a0e05-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/1c4b4f02b114574a0e05-510x383.jpg 510w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/1c4b4f02b114574a0e05-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/1c4b4f02b114574a0e05-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/08\/1c4b4f02b114574a0e05.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1293px) 100vw, 1293px\" title=\"\"><strong><em>R\u00e8m c\u1eeda 2 l\u1edbp ki\u1ec3u may Ore<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 110%; color: #000080;\"><strong><em>C\u1ea3 v\u1ea3i v\u00e0 voan \u0111\u1ec1u may chi\u1ebft ly<\/em><\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\" wp-image-2897 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kieumaychietly-534x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1286\" height=\"964\" srcset=\"https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kieumaychietly-534x400.jpg 534w, https:\/\/remphuthanh.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/02\/kieumaychietly-510x382.jpg 510w, https:\/\/re